<whtranslation key="~whDemoShortDescfire">
Interbase Objects components are used to gain access to data in a Firebird SQL 
database.
</whtranslation>


<whtranslation key="~whDemoLongDescfire">
There are many ways to display and manipulate SQL data (of course). 
This demo tries to keep it simple, to teach you one good way. 
</whtranslation>

